docs {
  ## Get Peer Count

  Retrieve the number of peers by connection state.

  ### Response (200)
  ```json
  {
    "data": {
      "disconnected": "12",
      "connecting": "1",
      "connected": "44",
      "disconnecting": "0"
    }
  }
  ```
}
